WEBVTT

00:03:58.520 --> 00:04:00.040
not to set an alarm,

00:04:00.040 --> 00:04:02.480
but she understood what I wanted.

00:04:02.480 --> 00:04:05.490
We speak to each other like this.

00:04:05.560 --> 00:04:09.060
We say a bit, and one has 
to understand the rest.

00:04:09.200 --> 00:04:12.040
This AI can do a thousand such things.

00:04:12.040 --> 00:04:13.280
You want some music,

00:04:13.280 --> 00:04:16.660
she will choose 
from billions of songs for you.

00:04:16.720 --> 00:04:20.440
A lot of people say their AI 
has become a friend.

00:04:21.240 --> 00:04:25.160
She reads stories, tells them jokes,

00:04:25.160 --> 00:04:27.040
can help with studies as well.

00:04:27.980 --> 00:04:31.450
Alexa, who was 
the first president of India?